<div id="review_6667081" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/6667081" />
    <a title="Christy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/409348-christy"><img alt="Christy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1327367681p2/409348.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/6667081?book_show_action=true">Sep 23, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Christy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Christy" href="/user/show/409348-christy">Christy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">EVERYONE</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/409348-christy?shelf=goodcry">goodcry</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/409348-christy?shelf=historic-fiction">historic-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/409348-christy?shelf=favorite-authors">favorite-authors</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/409348-christy?shelf=best-books-ever">best-books-ever</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/409348-christy?shelf=re-read">re-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer6667081" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer422881025425803135">Truly one of the best books I&apos;ve ever read. The characters are so beautifully written, I felt like I knew Lifee and Mor. It&apos;s a book that doesn&apos;t leave your head when you put it down. It is thought provoking, heartbreaking and inspirational. Loved it!<br/><br/>I just re-read this and was sad to find I didn&apos;t love it quite as much. I still think Cooper is an excellent story teller and I still really cared about these characters, but it just wasn&apos;t as well written as I remember. I&apos;m leaving the ratings alon</span>
  <span id="freeText422881025425803135" style="display:none">Truly one of the best books I've ever read. The characters are so beautifully written, I felt like I knew Lifee and Mor. It's a book that doesn't leave your head when you put it down. It is thought provoking, heartbreaking and inspirational. Loved it!<br /><br />I just re-read this and was sad to find I didn't love it quite as much. I still think Cooper is an excellent story teller and I still really cared about these characters, but it just wasn't as well written as I remember. I'm leaving the ratings alone because it reflects how I felt when I first read it years ago. I still recommend it strongly, but I will say it is repetitive in parts and I had a harder time just accepting that Lifee would be that enlightened and strong.</span>
  <a data-text-id="422881025425803135" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


