          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44325803-bamboozlepig?shelf=drama">drama</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44325803-bamboozlepig?shelf=historical-novel">historical-novel</a>
