<span id="freeTextContainer12671447968748742603">Too didactic for me too really enjoy it. Especially in the dialogue. Also felt like the author was more telling me the story than showing me. Parts were enjoyable, but it was very slow. Very little conflict within the main characters. It wasn&apos;t believable to me that such a large group never disagreed on anything.</span>
